Class PersistableBundleCompat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.evernote.android.job.util.support.PersistableBundleCompat

  • public final class PersistableBundleCompat
extends Object
    Compat class which provides similar features like PersistableBundle. Besides a boolean array all methods are available.
